            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>昨日（10 月 1 日）中国庆祝成立 75 周年，中国深圳一连 7 日举行「天空之城大有可能」无人机表演，逾万架无人机在夜空进行灯光表演，吸引了大量当地民众观赏，龙岗、福田、罗湖、龙华及大鹏，都有无人机正常表演。同日香港举办的「中国国庆烟花汇演」亦首次加入无人机环节，但据悉因「电离层闪烁」影响无人机接收衞星定位讯号，最终表演告吹。无独有偶，香港原定于 9 月 30 日晚在维多利亚港上空举行「新生代千人合唱贺国庆」无人机表演，亦疑因太阳风暴干扰而取消。连同上月 21 日啬色园联同黄大仙民政事务处举办的《黄大仙宝诞·紫气龙腾耀香江—无人机汇演》，香港近期已经有 3 次同类型无人机表演临场取消。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266971" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002130225-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002130225-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002130225.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p>昨日（10 月 1 日）中国深圳如期举行无人机表演，无人机排列出巨龙、无人机、AI 晶片、中国深圳天际线等等图案，成为当地庆祝活动焦点。此次「天空之城大有可能」无人机表演将会结合深圳各个城市特色，由 10 月 1 日至 7 日每日在深圳 5 个地方空中演出。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266965" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125626-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125626-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125626.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳龙岗以无人机排列出巨龙图案，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266966" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125607-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125607-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125607.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳龙岗以无人机排列出无人机图案，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266967" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125538-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125538-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125538.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳龙岗亦以无人机排列出 AI 晶片图案，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266963" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125236-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125236-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125236.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳福田的无人机表演，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266970" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002130311-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002130311-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002130311.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳福田以无人机排列出天际线，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266964" src="https://cdn.un