mage-1266976" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131003-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131003-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131003.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳罗湖的无人机表演，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266977" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131201-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131201-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131201.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳罗湖的无人机表演，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266978" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131242-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131242-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131242.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳罗湖的无人机表演，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266979" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131434-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131434-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131434.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳龙华的无人机表演，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266980" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131355-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131355-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131355.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳龙华的无人机表演，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266981" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131603-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131603-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131603.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳龙华以无人机排列成巨龙形状，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266982" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131551-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131551-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131551.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳龙华的无人机表演，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266983" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131542-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131542-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131542.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳龙华的无人机表演，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266986" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131453-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131453-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131453.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳龙华的无人机表演，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266987" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131840-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131840-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131840.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国深圳大鹏的无人机表演，图片来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p>相比之下，香港原定于同日（10 月 1 日）在维港上空举行烟花汇演，另外亦是首次加插无人机飞行表演环节，惟康文署在当日晚上燃放烟花前宣布因维港上空出现「电离层闪烁」（ionospheric scintillation）现象而取消无人机环节目。</p><p>据《香港电台》引述天文台指，全球定位系统（Global Positioning System，GPS）无线电讯号需经过电离层传送讯息至地面接收站，以测量位置提供导航。如太阳活动强烈或会影响并干扰电离层，令测量位置讯息准确度下降。「电离层闪烁」是无线电波沿著讯号路径因电离层中电子密度的小尺度结构而产生的快速变化，严重情况下会影响 GPS 收发器锁定讯号，因此 10 月 1 日当天须取消烟花前的无人机表演环节。</p><p>香港 9 月 30 日的「新生代千人合唱贺国庆」无人机表演亦因「受到干扰出现故障」而取消，据大会表示，事件并不涉及人为干扰。天文台前助理台长、气象学会发言人梁荣武在《商业电台》节目表示，太阳风暴引起的电磁扰动，会影响地球磁场，精密仪器或会受到影响，影响飞行安全。</p><p>对于「新生代千人合唱贺国庆」取消无人机飞行一事，《独立媒体》引述梁荣武指对安排感到「小小奇怪」。梁荣武指，太阳风暴一般影响邻近南北极的地区，香港位处北纬 21 度南方，如果受到影响的话，相信今次太阳风暴非常强烈。虽然梁荣武认为威胁不大，但由于无人机表演涉及各种不同人因素，其形容大会取消表演是「风险管理」。</p><p>香港无人机表演取消后，市民反应不一。有些人对此感到失望，因为无法看到期待已久的灯光展示；但也有市民认为这是出于安全考量的正确决定。无人机在受干扰情况下可能无法正常飞行，存在潜在风险，取消活动是避免事故的必要措施。翻查纪录，今次已是近期第 3 次无人机飞行表演在无预警状态下取消。对上一次则是由啬色园联同黄大仙民政事务处举办的《黄大仙宝诞·紫气龙腾耀香江—无人机汇演》，原定于 9 月 21 日在湾仔海滨维港上空举行，及后因天雨影响而在原定表演开始时间一小时后临时宣布取消。</p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a>、<a href="https://www.i-cable.com/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A/275274/%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E9%81%87%E5%B9%B2%E6%93%BE%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E6%A2%81%E6%A6%AE%E6%AD%A6-%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E6%94%B9">i-Cable</a>、<a href="https://www.881903.com/news/local/2550272/%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E7%96%91%E5%9B%A0%E5%8F%97%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%96%E5%B9%B2%E6%93%BE%E8%A8%8A%E8%99%9F">商业电台</a>、<a href="https://www.singtaousa.com/2024-10-01/%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B675%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%EF%B8%B1%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B37%E5%A4%A95%E5%8D%80%E8%90%AC%E6%9E%B6%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94-%E5%A4%9C%E7%A9%BA%E5%B7%A8%E9%BE%8D%E7%82%BA/5010349">星岛</a>、<a href="https://www.inmediahk.net/node/%E6%94%BF%E7%B6%93/%E9%81%87%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E5%B9%B2%E6%93%BE%E9%9B%BB%E7%A3%81%E5%A0%B4-%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E6%B0%A3%E8%B1%A1%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83%E6%A2%81%E6%A6%AE%E6%AD%A6%EF%BC%9A%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86">独立媒体</a>、<a href="https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/1062102/%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6-2099%E6%9E%B6%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E9%81%87%E5%B9%B2%E6%93%BE%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE-%E4%BF%BE%E4%BD%A0%E6%94%BE%E5%92%97%E5%85%A9%E6%AC%A1%E9%A3%9B%E6%A9%9F">HK01</a>、<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1772986-20241002.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/05/%e7%84%a1%e4%ba%ba%e6%a9%9f%e8%a1%a8%e6%bc%94-7-7-%e8%b3%80-anson-lo-%e7%94%9f%e6%97%a5-%e6%ad%b7%e6%99%82-12-%e5%88%86%e9%90%98-%e6%8f%90%e4%be%9b%e5%85%8d%e8%b2%bb%e6%b8%a1%e8%bc%aa/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">无人机表演 7.7 贺 Anson Lo 生日，历时 12 分钟 + 提供免费渡轮</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/02/1-october-drones-performance-cancelled/life-tech/drone/">深圳 10.1 五个区无人机表演如常　香港无人机演出三度「放飞机」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
