        <item>
            <title>特色布质半敞篷车顶，雷诺 4 E-Tech electric 月中巴黎车展现身</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/02/renault-4-e-tech-electric/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=renault-4-e-tech-electric</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/02/renault-4-e-tech-electric/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 05:00:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Renault 4 E-Tech electric]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1266925</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>法国车厂雷诺（Renault）的 4 E-Tech electric 电动车将会在 10 月 14 日于巴黎车展上全球首发，雷诺日前率先公布了车辆的首批图片。虽然图片的数量颇多，不过并未有完整展示 4 E-Tech electric 的外观，因为雷诺希望在正式发布时才揭晓这部电动车的全貌。</p><p><span id="more-1266925"></span></p><p>从雷诺公开的图片，可以看到一些 4 E-Tech electric 的细节，例如带有背光效果的品牌徽章和前格栅，还有左侧车门下方的部分设计。图片还显示了车尾灯、泵把、代表 4 E-Tech electric 的「4」号徽章、车门后的侧窗、车顶与尾门交接的角度、车顶行李架和尾翼。雷诺 4 E-Tech electric 电动车的一大特色是可以打开的布制车顶，将会为驾驶者带来半敞篷的感觉。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=1266946" rel="attachment wp-att-1266946"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266946" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10021b-580x580.jpg" alt="Renault 4 E-Tech electric" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10021b-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10021b.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10021b-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>雷诺 4 E-Tech electric 的车身长度为 4,140mm，比早前公布 5 E-Tech electric 更长，两者皆使用相同的 AmpR Small 平台。消息指 4 E-Tech electric 将会在法国制造，明年就会正式上市。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.arenaev.com/renault_4_etech_electric_smiles_in_first_official_teaser_images-news-3976.php">arenaev</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/02/renault-4-e-tech-electric/life-tech/auto/">特色布质半敞篷车顶，雷诺 4 E-Tech electric 月中巴黎车展现身</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
